snippet.title: Checkers (proto) - (1980?) - Bally Astrocade - WIN!
snippet.description:
Bally Midway © 1980?
[Console] Bally Astrocade
Emulator: MAME 0.226

A prototype cartridge, and no official release is yet known.  It's actually not too bad, although the AI could use some serious improvement.  But I liked that it was a QUICK game of checkers… and I guess I kinda liked smoking the computer with hardly much thought.  Guess a prototype computer opponent isn't all bad.
